data.name: memoEdit1.EditValue
data.value:
Please note that Trionic 5 does not support bi-fuelling. Once your binary has been converted to E85 it will no longer run on regular petrol.
The wizard will alter ignition settings, cranking and afterstart fuelling and normal fuelling.

data.name: memoEdit2.EditValue
data.value: Please note that coldstart and warmup factors are estimated. You might need to do some tweaking to get it all spot on. Furthermore, please assure yourself that the fuel mixture is correct by measuring it with a wideband lambda sensor.
